data.description: Lovely Craftsman Two Story 5 Bedroom 3.5 Bath Home with Finished Basement! Open Foyer leading to Large Dining Room and Family Room. Kitchen offers stainless steel appliances with white cabinets, walk-in pantry, granite counter-tops and large kitchen island. Hardwood floors throughout the kitchen and living area. Upper level of the home has a large laundry room and Master Suite with sitting/office area. Master bathroom has double vanity with separate tub, tiled Shower and walk-in closet. Full finished basement has a bedroom and full bathroom, an entertainment room with access to the backyard. Upper level has a large screened porch. 6 foot Privacy Fence wraps the beautifully landscaped private level backyard. Home is perfectly located at the end of the street in a cul-de-sac! The Community has a Clubhouse and Swimming Pool all located in Downtown Hoschton! Walk to Hoschton Park or the nearby shops & dining! Enjoy the holiday parades and celebrations right outside your front door! Easy access to I-85.
